  "name": "Medical Release Regenerate",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Medical.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You touch a creature and stimulate its natural healing ability. The target regains 4d8+15 hit points. For the duration of the jutsu, the target regains 1 hit point at the start of each of its turns (10 hit points per minute).</p><p>The targets severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to the stump, the jutsu instantly causes the limb to knit to the stump.</p>",
